body:
### json schemata for the gw2 api v2
This is a set of json schemata for the gw2 api v2.

Usages: 
- Clone Repo: 
```
$ git clone https://github.com/Tydal/gw2-json-schema.git
```
- Download source (see above) and use locally
- Reference schemata individually. https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Tydal/gw2-json-schema/master/{schema-name}
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
